data.meta_description:
3,830 likes, 41 comments - nobelprize_org on April 7, 2024: "Take a look at Gabriela Mistral receiving her Nobel Prize on 10 December 1945. 

She received the literature prize "for her lyric poetry which, inspired by powerful emotions, has made her name a symbol of the idealistic aspirations of the entire Latin American world." 

Read more by clicking the link in bio. 

Photo: Bettmann Via Getty Images. 

#NobelPrize".
